    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You have sworn an oath to protect and support your allies, which requires you to both defend them but also take aggressive actions. You gain the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-adventures-in-etheirys.actions.Item.lczkHT2svCEpGYaV]{Oath of Blades} and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-adventures-in-etheirys.actions.Item.D1B0CJtMuz6w4uxy]{Oath of Shields} actions, which allow you to take stances based on your swordplay and shield handling. Additionally, you gain the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-adventures-in-etheirys.actions.Item.Rpyad07uGnGakwlG]{Oath Shift} action, which allows you to more fluidly swap your oaths in the midst of battle.</p>",
